---
// Section 6: Data Retention
---

<div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
  <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">Section 6: Data Retention Policies</h2>

  <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400">Retention Schedule</h3>
  <table class="mb-6 w-full border-collapse text-sm">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th class="border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2.5 py-2 text-left text-white/90">Data Type</th>
        <th class="border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2.5 py-2 text-left text-white/90">Retention</th>
        <th class="border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2.5 py-2 text-left text-white/90">Notes</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">User accounts</td><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Until deletion + 30 days</td><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Soft delete, then purge</td></tr
      >
      <tr><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Server configurations</td><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Until server deleted</td><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Backed up daily</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Game server logs</td><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">7 days rolling</td><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">User-configurable up to 30</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Billing records</td><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">7 years</td><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Legal requirement</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Audit logs</td><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">90 days</td><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Security events</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Telemetry/metrics</td><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">30 days</td><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Performance data</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400">Backup Strategy</h3>
  <div class="mb-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-4">
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-white/70">
      <li>- Daily automated backups of all PostgreSQL databases</li>
      <li>- User-initiated game server backups stored in S3</li>
      <li>- Configuration snapshots on every change</li>
      <li>- 30-day backup retention by default</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400">Data Minimization</h3>
  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-indigo-500/35 bg-indigo-500/[0.12] p-4">
    <strong>Principle:</strong> Collect only what's necessary for service operation. No customer game
    data is stored unless explicitly backed up by the user.
  </div>
</div>
